00:40:42.720 --> 00:40:43.770
but I think any society.

00:40:43.770 --> 00:40:46.110
We have a lot of things that
are enforced by societies

00:40:46.110 --> 00:40:48.910
say that are counter--

00:40:48.910 --> 00:40:50.750
essentially not logical.

00:40:50.750 --> 00:40:55.830
And if you raise your child
to be a critical thinker--

00:40:55.830 --> 00:40:57.390
I'm trying to be
critical thinker.

00:40:57.390 --> 00:40:59.330
And I get a lot of
frustration out of that.

00:40:59.330 --> 00:41:01.087
